## NFTCollection.supplyOf() method

Get the supply of NFT editions minted from a specific NFT

**Signature:**

```typescript
supplyOf(nftAddress: string): Promise<number>;
```

## Parameters

| Parameter  | Type   | Description                                        |
| ---------- | ------ | -------------------------------------------------- |
| nftAddress | string | the mint address of the NFT to check the supply of |

**Returns:**

Promise&lt;number&gt;

the supply of the specified NFT

## Example

```jsx
const address = "...";
const supply = await program.supplyOf(address);
```
